OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,FThe Nottingham Inquiry into the
OL,7,Fattacks of 2023 has heard that a
OL,8,Fconsultant psychiatrist warned that
OL,9,FValdo Calocane would "end up killing
OL,10,Fsomeone" after violent incidents three
OL,11,Fyears before the attacks.
OL,13,FEvidence presented to the inquiry on
OL,14,FWednesday included medical notes
OL,15,Frecording that Calocane showed no
OL,16,Fsigns of remorse or insight in 2020,
OL,17,Fafter in incident where a woman was so
OL,18,Fscared of him she jumped out of a
OL,19,Ffirst floor window.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
