CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,FThe inquiry in central London ,was
OL,7,Ftold the woman required surgery for a
OL,8,Ffractured vertebrae after an incident
OL,9,Fat student accommodation in the
OL,10,FRadford area of Nottingham.
OL,12,FCalocane killed University of
OL,13,FNottingham students Barnaby Webber and
OL,14,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,15,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,16,Fattempted to kill three more people in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
