OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,FThe inquiry has previously heard a
OL,7,Fwarrant to arrest the violent
OL,8,Fschizophrenic was not executed by
OL,9,Fpolice for months before the attacks,
OL,10,Fin what was described as a "serious,
OL,11,Fsystemic, operational failure".
OL,13,FWatch in full: Nottingham attack
OL,14,Fvictims' families and survivors give
OL,15,Femotional impact statements
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
