OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]tD@WOUxD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,F"I would have been concerned very much
OL,7,Fabout the lack of remorse"
OL,9,FThe witness agreed with Mr Blake that
OL,10,Finformation contained in the medical
OL,11,Fnotes was "highly relevant to the
OL,12,Funiversity".
OL,14,FShe added: "I think it's most
OL,15,Fimportant for the mental health team
OL,16,Fthat are managing him because they are
OL,17,Fthe people that are responsible for
OL,18,Fhis care and treatment.
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@KO]vD@LOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,F"What we would do in those situations,
OL,7,Fif that was shared with us, and we
OL,8,Fwere able to work positively with the
OL,9,Fstudent, we would absolutely encourage
OL,10,Fthem to take their medication and to
OL,11,Fengage fully with the services.
OL,13,F"And we always are very clear that
OL,14,Fpeople need to put their mental health
OL,15,Fand wellbeing first.
OL,17,F"I think what would have stood out to
OL,18,Fme had I seen this before, I would
OL,19,Fhave been concerned very much about
OL,20,Fthe lack of remorse.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772132672
OL,3,CUniversity not told of psychiatrist's
OL,4,Cconcerns that Valdo Calocane might kill
OL,6,F"Often when your people are recovering
OL,7,F(from psychosis) one of the things you
OL,8,Fhave to work with someone about is how
OL,9,Fthey feel, because they will often
OL,10,Ffeel very remorseful and bad about
OL,11,Fwhat's happened.
OL,13,F"A lack of remorse... is something
OL,14,Fthat would have been useful for
OL,15,Feverybody to think about carefully."
OL,17,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
